<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="reply-v">reply <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /rɪ'plaɪ/    美 /rɪ'plaɪ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>回答；答复：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>reply to</strong> a question 
回答问题</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He <strong>replied that</strong> he knew nothing about it. 
他回答说对此一无所知。</p></div></div>